          <tr><td>Fitness</td><td>14-17%</td><td>Fit appearance; some muscle definition; healthy and sustainable long-term</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Average</td><td>18-24%</td><td>Typical for healthy men; no visible abs but generally good health markers</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Obese</td><td>25%+</td><td>Elevated health risks; associated with metabolic syndrome and cardiovascular disease</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

